{htxt id='id-adjust-financial-type'}
  <p>{ts domain="de.systopia.contract"}Set the financial type of all contributions to the financial type specified in the selected contract's type.{/ts}</p>
{/htxt}

{htxt id='id-re-assign'}
  <p>{ts domain="de.systopia.contract"}If selected even already assigned contributions will be detached from their current contract, and re-assigned to the selected one.{/ts}</p>
{/htxt}

{htxt id='id-assign-mode'}
  <p>{ts domain="de.systopia.contract"}Here you can select to assign the contributions not only to the membership but also to the recurring contribution (e.g. standing order).{/ts}</p>
  <p>{ts domain="de.systopia.contract"}This option is only available for non-SEPA contracts, and will only be executed for non-SEPA contributions.{/ts}</p>
{/htxt}

{htxt id='id-adjust-pi'}
  <p>{ts domain="de.systopia.contract"}Adjust the payment instrument of all assigned contributions.{/ts}</p>
{/htxt}
